'''性病学'''（{{lang-en|Venereology}}）是研究和治疗[[性傳染病|性传播疾病]]的医学分支。性病学这个词语来源于[[古罗马|古罗马]]女神[[维纳斯|维纳斯]]，她主宰爱情、美丽和生育能力。性病专科医生被称为性病学家。<ref>{{cite web |title=Venerologist |url=https://medical-dictionary.thefreedictionary.com/venereologist |website=The Free Dictionary |access-date=2021-01-31 |archive-date=2021-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210205095919/https://medical-dictionary.thefreedictionary.com/venereologist |dead-url=no }}</ref>在世界许多国家和地区，性病学专科通常属[[皮肤病学|皮肤病学]]科。<ref>{{cite web |title=Journal of the European Academy of Dermatology and Venerology |url=https://www.wiley.com/en-us/Journal+of+the+European+Academy+of+Dermatology+and+Venereology-p-9780JRNL61760 |publisher=Wiley |access-date=2021-01-31 |archive-date=2018-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181203060305/https://www.wiley.com/en-us/Journal+of+the+European+Academy+of+Dermatology+and+Venereology-p-9780JRNL61760 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

性病包括[[细菌|细菌]]、[[病毒|病毒]]、[[真菌|真菌]]和[[寄生虫|寄生虫]]感染。<ref>{{cite web|title=List of all STDs and their Symptoms|url=https://www.std-gov.org/stds/std_list.htm|date=2017-03-28|access-date=2021-01-31|archive-date=2018-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180630162037/https://www.std-gov.org/stds/std_list.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>一些重要的疾病如：[[艾滋病|艾滋病毒感染]]、[[梅毒|梅毒]]、[[淋病|淋病]]、[[念珠菌症|念珠菌症]]、[[单纯疱疹|单纯疱疹]]、[[人类乳头瘤病毒|人类乳头瘤病毒]]感染和[[生殖器|生殖器]][[疥疮|疥疮]]。性病学领域研究还包括[[软下疳|软下疳]]、[[花柳性淋巴肉芽腫|花柳性淋巴肉芽肿]]、[[腹股沟肉芽肿|腹股沟肉芽肿]]、[[乙型肝炎|乙型肝炎]]和[[巨细胞病毒|巨细胞病毒]]感染。<ref>{{cite web |title=What you need to know about STDs |url=https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/246491.php |website=Medical News Today |access-date=2021-01-31 |archive-date=2019-09-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190902085123/https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/246491.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>

